### 1. The Database Schema (`prisma/schema.prisma`)

We need a relationship between Categories and Businesses.

```prisma
generator client {
  provider = "prisma-client-js"
}

datasource db {
  provider = "postgresql"
  url      = env("DATABASE_URL")
}

model Category {
  id         String     @id @default(cuid())
  name       String     @unique
  slug       String     @unique
  businesses Business[]
}

model Business {
