### 5. Advanced Indexing (Raw SQL Migration)
To keep the backend fast as the database grows, you should add a **GIN Index** to the JSONB column. Prisma doesn't support GIN indexes natively in the schema file yet, so we add it via a migration.

```sql
-- prisma/migrations/xxx_add_gin_index.sql
CREATE INDEX property_attributes_idx ON "Property" USING GIN (attributes);
```

